{
  "page": "Cosgrove",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Cosgrove</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>Steward of <a href=\"/index.php/Whitewalls\" title=\"Whitewalls\">Whitewalls</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_the_games\" title=\"Master of the games\">Master of the games</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Butterwell\" title=\"House Butterwell\">House Butterwell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Mystery_Knight\" title=\"The Mystery Knight\">The Mystery Knight</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Cosgrove</b> was the steward of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Butterwell\" title=\"House Butterwell\">House Butterwell</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys I Targaryen\">Aerys I Targaryen</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cosgrove&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_tourney_at_Whitewalls\" title=\"Wedding tourney at Whitewalls\">wedding tourney at Whitewalls</a>, Cosgrove acted as the <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_the_games\" title=\"Master of the games\">master of the games</a>. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a> sent his squire, <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Egg</a>, to meet with Cosgrove and enter the <a href=\"/index.php/Hedge_knight\" title=\"Hedge knight\">hedge knight</a> in the lists as a <a href=\"/index.php/Mystery_knight\" title=\"Mystery knight\">mystery knight</a> called the Gallows Knight.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Uthor_Underleaf\" title=\"Uthor Underleaf\">Uthor Underleaf</a> bribed Cosgrove for favorable matches.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Cosgrove was reluctant to admit Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Glendon_Flowers\" title=\"Glendon Flowers\">Glendon Flowers</a> to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Ambrose_Butterwell\" title=\"Ambrose Butterwell\">Ambrose Butterwell</a>'s feast within <a href=\"/index.php/Whitewalls\" title=\"Whitewalls\">Whitewalls</a>, insisting that Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Quentyn_Ball\" title=\"Quentyn Ball\">Quentyn Ball</a> did not have a son and disregarding Glendon's claim of having been knighted by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Morgan_Dunstable\" title=\"Morgan Dunstable\">Morgan Dunstable</a>. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Kirby_Pimm\" title=\"Kirby Pimm\">Kirby Pimm</a> spoke with Cosgrove, however, and Glendon was eventually allowed to attend the feast. <sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cosgrove&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Cosgrove is as fond of <a href=\"/index.php/Silver\" title=\"Silver\">silver</a> as the next man.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Uthor_Underleaf\" title=\"Uthor Underleaf\">Uthor Underleaf</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cosgrove&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.